Is uncompleted even a word? "A reviewer"? shouldn't it be "The review" or "This review"?

Comments from most M4 planning session:

{quote}
need to continue to support existing column sorting and grouping by branch.  need to continue to support anchoring to revision and branch. consider an iframe approach before we go for pagination. build.xml is the pathological case. 
most complex scenario - get data via ajax with server side sorting/pagination
{quote}


This cannot be just client side pagination - maybe....  Need a way to go straight to the latest revisions for a given branch.  First pass is to return all revisions in json and only display a page full on the client.  This is based on the assumption that generating the json serverside is cheap.  What about diffs between revisions on different pages?
